title: The Woods Tea Co. - Live: Collector's Edition (320)
description:
The Woods Tea Co. - Live! Collector's Edition - (320)

A US traditional and folk music group formed in 1981.  I'm not sure how I discovered them, but if you like folk music they're worth a listen.
